    path: /workspace/PF5-to-PF6-Migration-Checklist.md
    content: # PatternFly 5 → PatternFly 6: Comprehensive Migration Checklist

> **Source**: Official PatternFly upgrade guide (https://www.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade/), pf-codemods README, and release notes.
>
> **Prerequisite**: Complete the PF4→PF5 migration first if not done already.
>
> **Automation**: Run `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path> --v6` then add `--fix` for auto-fixes. Many items below are handled by codemods, but manual review is always required.

---

## A. Package / Dependency Changes

### A1. Version Bumps
- [ ] `@patternfly/react-core` → `^6.x`
- [ ] `@patternfly/react-table` → `^6.x`
- [ ] `@patternfly/react-charts` → `^6.x`
- [ ] `@patternfly/react-icons` → `^6.x`
- [ ] `@patternfly/react-tokens` → `^6.x`
- [ ] `@patternfly/react-styles` → `^6.x`
- [ ] `@patternfly/patternfly` (CSS) → `^6.x`
- [ ] `@patternfly/react-component-groups` → `^6.x` (if used)
- [ ] `@patternfly/react-drag-drop` — new package for drag-and-drop (replaces deprecated DragDrop)

### A2. New Peer Dependencies
- [ ] `victory` (or specific victory-* packages) — now an **optional peer dependency** for `@patternfly/react-charts`. Install explicitly if you use charts.

### A3. Removed/Deprecated Packages & Paths
- [ ] `@patternfly/react-core/next` — promoted components moved to `@patternfly/react-core`
- [ ] `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` — old implementations moved here (Modal, DualListSelector, DragDrop, Chip, Tile, etc.)

---

## B. Component API Changes

### B1. EmptyState — Major Refactor ⚠️ (partially manual)
- [ ] `EmptyStateHeader` and `EmptyStateIcon` are now rendered **internally** within `EmptyState`
- [ ] `titleText` prop → pass directly to `<EmptyState titleText="...">`
- [ ] `headingLevel` prop → pass directly to `<EmptyState headingLevel="h4">`
- [ ] `icon` prop → pass icon component (not `<EmptyStateIcon>`) to `<EmptyState icon={CubesIcon}>`
- [ ] Remove standalone `<EmptyStateHeader>` and `<EmptyStateIcon>` elements
- [ ] `EmptyStateHeader`, `EmptyStateIcon` — no longer exported as standalone usage components

### B2. Modal — Deprecated & Replaced
- [ ] Old `Modal` from `@patternfly/react-core` → moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`
- [ ] `Modal` from `@patternfly/react-core/next` → promoted to `@patternfly/react-core`
- [ ] Recommendation: Use the new composable Modal from `@patternfly/react-core`

### B3. DualListSelector — Deprecated & Replaced
- [ ] Old `DualListSelector` → moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`
- [ ] `DualListSelector` from `@patternfly/react-core/next` → promoted to `@patternfly/react-core`

### B4. Button Changes
- [ ] `isActive` prop → renamed to `isClicked`
- [ ] Icons in plain buttons: must now be passed via `icon` prop, **not** as children
  - Old: `<Button variant="plain"><SomeIcon /></Button>`
  - New: `<Button variant="plain" icon={<SomeIcon />} />`
- [ ] `isDisabled` now sets `disabled` attribute (not `aria-disabled`) for `component="button"`
- [ ] `aria-disabled` only renders when `true` (no longer renders `aria-disabled="false"`)
- [ ] Button text now wrapped in `<span class="pf-v6-c-button__text">` — use `byRole` in tests instead of `byText`

### B5. Dropdown/Select/Menus — Deprecated Components Removed
- [ ] **Deprecated Dropdown** (from `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`) — removed entirely
- [ ] **Deprecated Select** — removed entirely
- [ ] **Deprecated Options Menu** — removed entirely
- [ ] **Application Launcher** — removed; use custom menu example
- [ ] **Context Selector** — removed; use custom menu example
- [ ] **KebabToggle** — removed; use `MenuToggle` with `variant="plain"`
- [ ] **Page Header** — removed; use `Masthead` + `Toolbar`

### B6. Chip → Label
- [ ] `Chip` component deprecated → moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`
- [ ] Recommended replacement: `Label` with `variant="outline"`
- [ ] `Chip` props mapping:
  - `onClick` → `onClose`
  - `badge` → render as child
  - `numChips` → `numLabels`
- [ ] `ChipGroup` → `LabelGroup`

### B7. Label Changes
- [ ] `isOverflowLabel` prop → replaced with `variant="overflow"`
- [ ] Color prop: `"cyan"` → `"teal"`, `"gold"` → `"yellow"`

### B8. Flex/FlexItem Changes
- [ ] `spacer` prop → replaced with `gap`, `columnGap`, or `rowGap`
- [ ] `spaceItems` prop → removed (use `gap` instead)

### B9. FormGroup Changes
- [ ] `labelIcon` prop → renamed to `labelHelp`
- [ ] Recommend using `FormGroupLabelHelp` element for the `labelHelp` prop

### B10. Nav Changes
- [ ] `variant="tertiary"` → `variant="horizontal-subnav"`
- [ ] `theme` prop → removed (use light/dark mode theming instead)

### B11. NavItem Changes
- [ ] `hasNavLinkWrapper` prop → removed

### B12. Tabs Changes
- [ ] `isSecondary` prop → renamed to `isSubtab`
- [ ] `variant="light300"` → `variant="secondary"`

### B13. Banner Changes
- [ ] `variant` prop → removed; use `color` or `status` props instead
  - `variant="red"` → `color="red"`
  - `variant="default"` → remove prop entirely
- [ ] Color prop: `"cyan"` → `"teal"`, `"gold"` → `"yellow"`

### B14. Expandable Section
- [ ] `isActive` prop → removed

### B15. Accordion Changes
- [ ] `AccordionContent` — `isHidden` prop removed (auto-set by `isExpanded` on AccordionItem)
- [ ] `AccordionToggle` — `isExpanded` prop moved to `AccordionItem`
- [ ] `AccordionItem` now renders a wrapping `div`

### B16. Avatar Changes
- [ ] `border` prop → removed; use `isBordered` instead

### B17. Card Changes
- [ ] Props removed: `isSelectableRaised`, `isDisabledRaised`, `hasSelectableInput`, `selectableInputAriaLabel`, `onSelectableInputChange`, `isFlat`, `isRounded`
- [ ] Clickable card: `selectableActions.name` and `selectableActions.selectableActionId` no longer needed

### B18. Checkbox & Radio Changes
- [ ] `isLabelBeforeButton` prop → replaced with `labelPosition="start"`

### B19. Drawer Changes
- [ ] `DrawerHead` — `hasNoPadding` prop removed
- [ ] `DrawerContent` — `colorVariant="no-background"` removed; `"primary"` value added
- [ ] `DrawerColorVariant` enum → use `DrawerContentColorVariant` or string values
- [ ] `DrawerPanelContent` — `colorVariant="light-200"` → `"secondary"`

### B20. Switch Changes
- [ ] `labelOff` prop → removed

### B21. HelperTextItem Changes
- [ ] `hasIcon` and `isDynamic` props → removed (icon auto-renders when `variant` is not "default")

### B22. DataListAction Changes
- [ ] `isPlainButtonAction` prop → removed

### B23. Page Changes
- [ ] `header` prop → renamed to `masthead`
- [ ] `isTertiaryNavGrouped` → renamed
- [ ] `isTertiaryNavWidthLimited` → renamed
- [ ] `tertiaryNav` → renamed
- [ ] `PageNavigation` component → removed
