## C. CSS / Styling Changes

### C1. Class Name Prefix Change
- [ ] `pf-v5-c-*` → `pf-v6-c-*` (components)
- [ ] `pf-v5-l-*` → `pf-v6-l-*` (layouts)
- [ ] `pf-v5-u-*` → `pf-v6-u-*` (utilities)
- [ ] Run: `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods/class-name-updater --v6 --fix`

### C2. Design Token System (New)
- [ ] PF5 CSS variables (`--pf-v5-*`) → PF6 design tokens (`--pf-t--*` for global, `--pf-v6-c-*` for component)
- [ ] Old global variables removed/renamed — **~50% of tokens replaced**
- [ ] Example: `--pf-v5-global--FontSize--lg` → `--pf-t--global--font--size--lg`
- [ ] CSS overrides targeting old variables will **silently fail** — remove or update all overrides
- [ ] Run: `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods/css-vars-updater` for .css/.scss/.md files

### C3. React Token Changes
- [ ] Old format: `global_FontSize_lg` → New format: `t_global_font_size_lg`
- [ ] Old format: `global_link_Color_hover` → find appropriate PF6 token
- [ ] Color tokens renamed: e.g. `color_green_10` → new token path
- [ ] Run: `tokens-update` codemod for .js/.tsx files
- [ ] Tokens with no 1:1 match will be set to `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` (hot pink) — must be manually resolved

### C4. Breakpoints — Now in `rem` (not `px`)
| Breakpoint | Token | Old (px) | New (rem) |
|---|---|---|---|
| xs | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--xs` | 0px | 0rem |
| sm | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--sm` | 576px | 36rem |
| md | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--md` | 768px | 48rem |
| lg | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--lg` | 992px | 62rem |
| xl | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--xl` | 1200px | 75rem |
| 2xl | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--2xl` | 1450px | 90.625rem |

- [ ] Update any hardcoded pixel-based breakpoint logic (divide px by 16)

### C5. Removed/Added Variables
- [ ] Check the official removed variables list: [Removed Variables Spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=1160160856&single=true)
- [ ] Check the official added variables list: [Added Variables Spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=268831450&single=true)

### C6. OUIA Attributes
- [ ] `data-ouia-component-type="PF5/*"` → `"PF6/*"`

