## E. Behavioral Changes

### E1. Button `isDisabled` Behavior
- [ ] `isDisabled` now sets native `disabled` attribute (not `aria-disabled`) when `component="button"`
- [ ] `aria-disabled` only renders when value is `true` (no longer renders `aria-disabled="false"`)
- [ ] Tests using `aria-disabled` for buttons will fail — update to check `disabled` attribute instead

### E2. Button Text Wrapping
- [ ] Button children now wrapped in `<span class="pf-v6-c-button__text">`
- [ ] RTL `byText` queries return the span, not the button — use `byRole('button', { name: '...' })` instead

### E3. Select Popper Behavior
- [ ] React Testing Library may not find menu options after selection if Popper menu is `aria-disabled`
- [ ] Fix: pass `{ hidden: true }` option or set `appendTo="inline"`

### E4. Accordion Markup
- [ ] `AccordionItem` now renders a wrapping `div` element

### E5. DrawerHead Markup
- [ ] Updated internal markup — snapshot tests will need updating

### E6. EmptyState Internals
- [ ] `EmptyStateHeader` and `EmptyStateIcon` now render internally — any tests or CSS targeting their old positions will break

### E7. Theming
- [ ] Component-level theming props removed (`theme`, `backgroundColor`, `border` for dark/light)
- [ ] Use CSS-level light/dark mode theming instead

### E8. Enable Animations
- [ ] Animation-related changes — check `enable-animations` codemod rule

