## F. Removal / Deprecation Summary

### F1. Components Removed Entirely (from all paths)
| Component | Replacement |
|---|---|
| Application Launcher | Custom menu example |
| Context Selector | Custom menu example |
| Deprecated Dropdown | Composable Dropdown or Dropdown template |
| Options Menu | Composable Select or Select template |
| Deprecated Select | Composable Select or Select template |
| Page Header | Masthead + Toolbar |
| KebabToggle | MenuToggle with `variant="plain"` |

### F2. Components Deprecated (moved to `/deprecated`)
| Component | Recommended Replacement |
|---|---|
| Chip / ChipGroup | Label / LabelGroup |
| Tile | Card |
| Modal (old) | Modal (new composable) |
| DualListSelector (old) | DualListSelector (new composable) |
| DragDrop / Droppable / Draggable | DragDropSort from `@patternfly/react-drag-drop` |

### F3. Props Removed
| Component | Prop Removed |
|---|---|
| AccordionContent | `isHidden` |
| Avatar | `border` |
| Banner | `variant` |
| Button | `isActive` (renamed to `isClicked`) |
| Card | `isSelectableRaised`, `isDisabledRaised`, `hasSelectableInput`, `selectableInputAriaLabel`, `onSelectableInputChange`, `isFlat`, `isRounded` |
| DataListAction | `isPlainButtonAction` |
| DrawerHead | `hasNoPadding` |
| ExpandableSection | `isActive` |
| HelperTextItem | `hasIcon`, `isDynamic` |
| Label | `isOverflowLabel` (→ `variant="overflow"`) |
| Masthead | `backgroundColor` |
| Nav | `theme` |
| NavItem | `hasNavLinkWrapper` |
| Page | `header` (renamed to `masthead`) |
| PageSection | Most `variant` values |
| PageSidebar | `theme` |
| Switch | `labelOff` |
| Toolbar | `usePageInsets` |
| ToolbarContent | `alignSelf` |
| ToolbarItem | `widths` |
| ToolbarToggleGroup | `alignment` |
| ToolbarGroup/Item/ToggleGroup | `spacer` (→ `gap`) |
| ToolbarGroup/ToggleGroup | `spaceItems` |

### F4. Interfaces/Types Removed or Renamed
| Old Name | New Name |
|---|---|
| `ToolbarChipGroupContentProps` | `ToolbarLabelGroupContentProps` |
| `ToolbarChipGroup` | `ToolbarLabelGroup` |
| `ToolbarChip` | `ToolbarLabel` |
| `TextProps` | `ContentProps` |
| `TextVariants` | `ContentVariants` |
| `TextListVariants` | removed |
| `TextListItemVariants` | removed |
| `PageSectionTypes` | removed |
| `PageSectionVariants` | reduced to `"default"` / `"secondary"` |
| `InvalidObjectProps` | `MissingPageProps` |
| `FormFiledGroupHeaderTitleTextObject` | `FormFieldGroupHeaderTitleTextObject` |
| `LogSnippetBorderVariant` | Use `AlertVariant` |

