## G. Migration Steps (Recommended Order)

1. [ ] **Update `package.json`** — bump all `@patternfly/*` packages to v6; install `victory` if using charts
2. [ ] **Run codemods** — `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <src> --v6` (review output)
3. [ ] **Run codemods with fix** — add `--fix` flag; review all changes
4. [ ] **Run class-name-updater** — `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods/class-name-updater --v6 --fix`
5. [ ] **Run tokens-update** — updates React tokens in .js/.tsx files
6. [ ] **Run css-vars-updater** — updates CSS variables in .css/.scss/.md files
7. [ ] **Remove CSS overrides** — temporarily remove all, see what still looks correct
8. [ ] **Update remaining CSS overrides** — map old variables to new design tokens
9. [ ] **Update breakpoint logic** — convert px values to rem
10. [ ] **Fix remaining build errors** — especially React token imports with no 1:1 mapping
11. [ ] **Update tests** — button `aria-disabled` changes, `byText` → `byRole`, snapshot updates
12. [ ] **Run data-codemods-cleanup** — `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <src> --v6 --only data-codemods-cleanup --fix`
13. [ ] **Visual review** — check all pages for hot-pink `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` markers indicating unresolved tokens
14. [ ] **Build and test**

