## H. Codemod Tools Reference

| Tool | Purpose | Command |
|---|---|---|
| **pf-codemods** | Main React component migration | `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path> --v6 --fix` |
| **class-name-updater** | `pf-v5-*` → `pf-v6-*` CSS class names | See [README](https://github.com/patternfly/pf-codemods/tree/main/packages/class-name-updater) |
| **tokens-update** | React token updates in .js/.tsx | Part of pf-codemods |
| **css-vars-updater** | CSS variable updates in .css/.scss/.md | See [README](https://github.com/patternfly/pf-codemods/tree/main/packages/css-vars-updater) |
| **data-codemods-cleanup** | Remove `data-codemods` markers | `--only data-codemods-cleanup` |

